Description: Limestone ostracon: on the recto eight incomplete lines of a duplicate text of P. Anastasi 1,3 (the interpolation). On the verso a few unintelligible signs only.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: H.-W.Fischer-Elfert, 'Die Satirische Streitschrift des Papyrus Anastasi' I, ‘Kleine ägyptische Texte’ (2nd edn, Wiesbaden 1992), pp.4 (no.81) and 39-42.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (393740) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/393740)
